IN BESTER LAGE in der inneren Stadt sind
einige grössere und kleinere Wohnungen zu vermiethen.
Jeder Comfort geboten. I., St. Annahof. Auskünfte
daselbst bei der Hausverwaltung und beim Portier.
A wealthy gentleman, who owns a country seat,
on one occasion nearly lost bis wife, who feil into a river
which flows through his estate. He announced the narrow
escape to his friends, expecting their congratulations. One
of them— an old bachelor— wrote as follows: »I al-
ways told you that river was too shallow.«
*
An old sea captain, under the impression that he
was saying a good thing, asked a lady passenger why
men never kiss one another, while ladies waste a world
of kisses on feminine faces.
»Because,« the lady replied, »the men have something
better to kiss, and the women haven’t.«
The captain saw the point.
